                                   -------------------
                                     git hube repo
                                           |
                                         clone
                                           |
                                        changes
                                           |
                                         commit
                                           |
                                          push

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

#GIT BRANCHES
git branch------------------>To check branch
git branch -M main------------->Reaneme branch
git checkout <branchname>--------->To navigate
git checkout -b <new branchname>----->To create a new branch
git branch -d <branchname>-------------->to delete branch

